{"tid":1541593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先六點幾灣仔嗰位手足","createTime":"2019-09-04T15:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:38:06.000Z","uid":279278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a11967cef2d3ce909b077b0f842088cbd2580b31","tid":1541593,"uid":279278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:18:35.000Z","msg":"頭先見有咁多人照顧住你所以行開咗<br />\n希望你會見到呢個post 想同你講：<br />\n<br />\n雖然路好難行 但係唔好忘記好多香港人都會同你一齊行落去㗎 我哋一齊手拖手行落去好無?  <br />\n<br />\n無嘢驚 最怕係少多個手足同我哋見證香港人勝利一刻<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">應承我 要陪我哋等到嗰一日</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61c244c22fe14a3b1b7ed6563a6c76afaa2a3cf6","tid":1541593,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},{"pid":"716b64b3a2847550755e4b66f7aa75ad36661a19","tid":1541593,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cfc3c63eaccfe593cf9f94764fd484e4cfac848","tid":1541593,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日<br />\n全民<span style=\"color: gold;\">入機場</span>揸春袋</strong>[/center<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKEJfno.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKEJfno.png&h=5aef9e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[center]<strong>9月8日<br />\n全民去<span style=\"color: pink;\">美國領事館請求通過人權法</span></strong></div><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m3ZhjO4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm3ZhjO4.png&h=538502ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"bad88cb3a610ef360070e57d9eacd726faf74993","tid":1541593,"uid":170504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:27:59.000Z","msg":"手足們 夠啦 頂唔順<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1541142\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1541142</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac374a76b8a83953c6da139f65cd37fd13451290","tid":1541593,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:38:06.000Z","msg":"睇到喇...<br />\n<br />\n多謝你"}]}